title: Motley Fool Money: 10.31.2014
description: On this week's show, our analysts discuss earnings news from Facebook, GoPro, LinkedIn, MasterCard, and Starbucks.  And Lawrence Cunningham talks about his new book, Berkshire Beyond Buffett:  The Enduring Value of Values.
